{"tid":1198646,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"香港的Big Picture","createTime":"2019-06-10T09:49:21.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-10T10:37:44.000Z","uid":188428,"like":5,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"ddd8b7b4c4efe6d3ba1b847fb59432e4da9ecab3","tid":1198646,"uid":188428,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-10T09:49:21.000Z","msg":"自古以嚟，大多成功嘅革命都係由流血同犧牲而成。<br />\n但係，香港存在以下項問題，令到阻止惡法推行，障礙重重。<br />\n<br />\n<strong><ins>行動派：無首、無策、無備</ins></strong><br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\">G蜂、天琦都不在了，誰能擔當行動派領袖？</div><br />\n<blockquote>......以928 我覺得G蜂算係咁，係佢先聚到學生同唔想用武力但想出力既人<br />\n天琦可以帶到班想勇武既人，各有各做根本perfect match<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<div style=\"text-align: right;\">節錄自：<strong><ins>香港真係好需要梁天琦</ins></strong>#8<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1197823/page/1\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1197823/page/1</a></div><br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong>無首</strong>，則<strong>無策</strong>。衝，則無勢。</div>尋晚一度有黃金機會，但民陣大台講明唔衝，亦冇其他組織/領袖號召市民衝，導致2000-2400期間，乜都唔係做緊。直至深夜，警察佈防極嚴時，示威者先至衝擊立法會，時勢不佳。<br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong>無備</strong>，即欠缺裝備。</div>親眼所見，尋晚嘅前排，連基本防裝都缺，自然抵受唔住防暴清場。<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong><ins>［好撚重要，廣傳］多圖抗爭手冊（裝備list）</ins></strong><br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1197512/page/1\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1197512/page/1</a></div><br />\n<br />\n<strong><ins>大局：香港人針拮唔到肉唔知痛</ins></strong><br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong><ins>陳浩天：大部份香港人唔係真係求生，只係希望死之前浪漫一下</ins></strong><a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1198011/page/1\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1198011/page/1</a></div><br />\n社會仍有大批中產，生活無憂，有樓揸手，有民可移。<br />\n喺有晒生活基礎之下，好難奢望佢哋會衝。<br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong><ins>大家可以學下亞美尼亞咁</ins></strong><br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1195636/page/1\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1195636/page/1</a></div><br />\n想和理非咁戰勝呢一仗？<br />\n要夠多人之餘，也要有公民抗命的覺悟，方能有起色。<br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">打最後呢一仗，大家都不期然有自己嘅包袱。<br />\n但係，請你本著「香港人」呢個名份，要搏盡。<br />\n行動嘅去馬，支援到嘅幫手，罷工罷市，唔好再猶疑喇。</span></strong></div>"},{"pid":"81ccdb03c5ecb1cbaf72affe9e52729da1f1cc96","tid":1198646,"uid":25858,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-10T09:51:13.000Z","msg":"香港大Picture<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bang.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3cbb8584edf94431551d4a9d7f408df39374e4df","tid":1198646,"uid":177082,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-10T10:05:00.000Z","msg":"無領首可以點<br />\n琴晚我留到4am都係灣仔<br />\n但係我見到嘅只係得一大班熱心但係好無計劃嘅人周圍亂衝走避警察<br />\n大家都有心但係唔知可以做啲咩"},{"pid":"91f1cd30dd76a5e24072d635ffc6874a5905ba4b","tid":1198646,"uid":188428,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"3cbb8584edf94431551d4a9d7f408df39374e4df","tid":1198646,"uid":177082,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-10T10:05:00.000Z","msg":"無領首可以點<br />\n琴晚我留到4am都係灣仔<br />\n但係我見到嘅只係得一大班熱心但係好無計劃嘅人周圍亂衝走避警察<br />\n大家都有心但係唔知可以做啲咩"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-10T10:27:54.000Z","msg":"大體嘅策略，其實尚算有，示威者想癱瘓道路。<br />\n敗筆在欠缺裝備，導致防暴走埋嚟時，根本冇得擋，只能節節敗退。<br />\n經歷咗6.9晚上/6.10凌晨一役，<br />\n值得問自己，為咗阻擋惡法，守護香港核心價值，<br />\n嚟緊呢幾日，香港人敢行到幾盡？"},{"pid":"905ec7f59e8939697c38367fddda34bd767e8135","tid":1198646,"uid":188428,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-10T10:28:38.000Z","msg":"推po"},{"pid":"154090618bf872c320130c1dda11ad345c2e4f2a","tid":1198646,"uid":188428,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-10T10:28:51.000Z","msg":"推po x2"},{"pid":"2b04bffe062a760a3ebf0fc3286fda4b687a55fc","tid":1198646,"uid":188428,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-10T10:29:08.000Z","msg":"推po x3"},{"pid":"1fb115b8b7752c5ce493d981a3d9954c2b38673f","tid":1198646,"uid":188428,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-10T10:29:28.000